https://www.anaconda.com/distribution/

Click on the above link: Go to Downloads (Select the type of OS: Windows/macOS/Linux)

Below I am installing in Linux Machine (Ubuntu 18.04.3 LTS)

$bash ~/Downloads/Anaconda3-2019.10-Linux-x86_64.sh

Follow the instructions..<Do..>

$anaconda-navigator
You can see Jupyter Notebook, Spyder, RStudio, Orange 3, Glueviz etc.




